    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014well-loved and super reliable for all your daily errands or weekend getaways. It runs like a dream and has been kept up beautifully, so it's ready to hit the road whenever you are. If you're looking for a dependable car that\u2019s been cared for, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great new home! \u2728",
