    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 1987 Porsche 911 Carrera 3.2 featuring the highly sought-after G50 5-speed manual transaxle with Borg-Warner synchronizers. The air-cooled flat-six power plant maintains excellent compression and delivers linear power through the Bosch Motronic fuel injection system. This chassis retains its original suspension configuration, utilizing longitudinal torsion bars and staggered Fuchs alloy wheels for authentic feedback and poise. The braking system is equipped with four-piston alloy calipers and vented rotors, ensuring reliable thermal management. While exhibiting minor cosmetic patina expected of an honest driver, the vehicle is structurally rigid and free of significant parasitic draws. This is a robust, analog machine ready for spirited canyon carving or long-distance touring.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
