      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and remains in impressive condition, perfect for someone seeking a reliable and well-maintained ride. The exterior features a deep, lustrous finish with only minor, expected road wear that doesn't detract from its overall curb appeal. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the leather upholstery is supple, and all electronic features\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system\u2014function exactly as they should. Mechanically, it's solid: the engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and it has a documented history of regular oil changes and scheduled maintenance. We recently fitted a new set of tires and performed a full brake service, so it\u2019s ready for the road immediately. It\u2019s a dependable, high-quality car that balances performance with comfort.",
